\c 7
\s UJesu wenyukela eJerusalema ngomkhosi wamadumba
\p
\v 1 Njalo emva kwalezizinto uJesu wayehamba eGalili; ngoba wayengathandi ukuhamba eJudiya\x + 11.54. 4.1,3.\x*, ngenxa\x + 5.16,18.\x* yokuthi amaJuda ayedinga ukumbulala\x + 7.11,13,15,35.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Wawusondele umkhosi wamaJuda wokwakha amadumba\x + Levi 23.34.\x*.
\v 3 Ngakho abafowabo bathi kuye: Suka lapha, uye eJudiya\x + Mat. 12.46.\x*, ukuze labafundi bakho babone imisebenzi yakho oyenzayo\x + 6.66.\x*.
\v 4 Ngoba kakho owenza ulutho ensitha, kodwa yena ngokwakhe edinga ukuba sobala. Uba uzenza lezizinto, ziveze wena emhlabeni\x + 1.31. 21.1.\x*.
\v 5 Ngoba labafowabo\x + Hlab. 69.8. Mark. 3.21.\x* babengakholwa kuye\x + Mat. 12.46.\x*.
\v 6 Ngakho uJesu wathi kubo: Isikhathi sami kasikafiki, kodwa esenu isikhathi sihlala silungile\x + 7.8,30. 2.4. 8.20. Mat. 26.18.\x*.
\v 7 Ungelizonde umhlaba lina; kodwa uyangizonda, ngoba mina ngifakaza ngawo\x + 15.18.\x*, ukuthi imisebenzi yawo mibi\x + 3.19.\x*.
\v 8 Yenyukelani lina emkhosini lo; mina angikenyukeli kulumkhosi\x + 7.10,14. Luka 2.4.\x*, ngoba isikhathi sami kasikagcwaliseki\x + Mark. 1.15.\x*\x + 7.8,30. 8.20. 2.4. Mat. 26.18.\x*.
\v 9 Esetshilo lezizinto kubo, wahlala eGalili.
\p
\v 10 Kodwa sebenyukile\x + 7.10,14. Luka 2.4.\x* abafowabo\x + Mat. 12.46.\x*, laye wasesenyukela emkhosini, kungeyisikho obala, kodwa kungathi \add ku\add*sensitha.
\v 11 AmaJuda\x + 11.56.\x* asemdinga emkhosini\x + 7.11,13,15,35.\x*, athi: Ungaphi yena?
\v 12 Kwakukhona ukukhonona okukhulu ngaye phakathi kwamaxuku\x + 7.43.\x*; abanye bathi: Ulungile\x + 6.14. 7.40.\x*. Kodwa abanye bathi: Hatshi, kodwa uyaliduhisa ixuku\x + 7.47.\x*.
\v 13 Loba kunjalo kwakungekho muntu owakhuluma obala ngaye ngokwesaba\x + 19.38. 20.19. 9.22. 12.42.\x* amaJuda\x + 7.11,13,15,35.\x*.
\s Imfundiso ngoKristu
\p
\v 14 Kuthe sekuphakathi komkhosi, uJesu wenyukela\x + 7.10,14. Luka 2.4.\x* ethempelini, wafundisa\x + 7.28.\x*.
\v 15 AmaJuda\x + 7.11,13,15,35.\x* asemangala athi\x + Mat. 13.54. Mark. 6.2,3. Luka 4.22.Joha. 7.46. Luka 2.47.\x*: Lo uyazi njani imibhalo, engafundanga?
\v 16 UJesu wawaphendula wathi: Imfundiso yami kayisiyo eyami kodwa ngeyalowo ongithumileyo\x + 3.34. 8.28. 12.49. 14.10,24.\x*.
\v 17 Uba umuntu ethanda ukwenza intando yakhe, uzakwazi ngemfundiso, ukuthi ivela kuNkulunkulu, kumbe ngizikhulumela mina ngokwami\x + 5.40. 8.43.\x*.
\v 18 Ozikhulumela ngokwakhe, uzidingela udumo lwakhe\x + 5.41.\x*; kodwa odinga udumo lwalowo omthumileyo, lowo uqinisile, njalo kakukho ukungalungi kuye\x + 5.41.\x*.
