\v 19 Kalinikanga yini uMozisi umlayo\x + 1.17. Dute. 31.10,11. Joha. 7.2.\x*, kanti kakho kini ogcina umlayo\x + 5.45. Luka 20.47.\x*? Lidingelani ukungibulala\x + 7.1,20,25. 5.16,18. 8.37,40. Mat. 12.14. Mark. 3.6. Joha. 10.39. 11.53.\x*?
\v 20 Ixuku laphendula lathi: Uledimoni\x + 8.48,52. 10.20. Mark. 3.22.\x*; ngubani odinga ukukubulala\x + 7.1,20,25. 5.16,18. 8.37,40. Mat. 12.14. Mark. 3.6. Joha. 10.39. 11.53.\x*?
