\v 25 Abanye kwabeJerusalema basebesithi: Lo kayisuye yini abadinga ukumbulala\x + 7.1,20,25. 5.16,18. 8.37,40. Mat. 12.14. Mark. 3.6. Joha. 10.39. 11.53.\x*?
