\v 27 Kodwa\x + Mat. 13.55.\x* lo siyazi lapho avela khona\x + Mat. 25.24.\x*; kodwa uKristu nxa efika, kakho ozakwazi lapho avela khona\x + Isa. 53.8. Joha. 7.42. 19.9.\x*.
\v 28 Ngakho uJesu efundisa ethempelini wamemeza\x + 7.14. Mat. 26.55.\x* wathi\x + 7.37.\x*: Lami liyangazi, liyakwazi lalapho engivela khona\x + 7.41. 8.14,19. 9.29.\x*; njalo kangizizelanga ngokwami\x + 8.42. 5.43.\x*, kodwa ongithumileyo uqinisile\x + 8.26. Roma 3.4. Joha. 5.32.\x*, elingamaziyo lina\x + 8.55.\x*.
