\v 30 Ngakho badinga ukumbamba\x + 7.44. 10.39. Mat. 21.46.\x*, kodwa kakubanga khona owabeka isandla phezu kwakhe\x + 7.44. 8.20. 19.7.\x*, ngoba ihola lakhe lalingakafiki\x + 12.23,27. 13.1. 17.1.\x*\x + 7.44. 8.20. 19.7.\x*.
