\v 31 Kodwa abanengi bexuku bakholwa kuye\x + 8.30.\x*, bathi: Nxa uKristu esefikile\x + Mat. 12.23.\x*, uzakwenza yini izibonakaliso ezinengi kulalezi azenzileyo lo\x + 3.2.\x*?
\v 32 AbaFarisi bezwa ixuku likhonona lezizinto ngaye; abapristi abakhulu labaFarisi basebethuma abancedisi ukuze bambambe\x + 7.45,46. Mat. 26.58.\x*.
\v 33 UJesu wasesithi kubo: Ngiselani okwesikhatshana\x + 12.35. 8.21.\x*, besengihamba ngiye kongithumileyo\x + 16.5.\x*.
\v 34 Lizangidinga, linga\add ngit\add*holi\x + 13.33. Hos. 5.6. Luka 17.22.\x*\x + 12.35.8.21.\x*, lalapho mina engikhona\x + 1.18. 3.13.\x*, lina lingeze leza\x + 13.36.\x*.
\v 35 Ngakho amaJuda akhulumisana \add athi\add*: Uzakuya ngaphi lo ukuthi thina singayikumthola\x + 7.1. 8.22.\x*? Kayikuya yini kwabahlakazekileyo bamaGriki, afundise amaGriki\x + Hlab. 147.2. Isa. 11.12. Jak. 1.1. 1 Pet. 1.1.\x*?
\v 36 Yilizwi bani leli alitshoyo \add elokuthi\add*: Lizangidinga, aliyiku\add ngi\add*thola; lelo\add kuthi\add*: Lapho engikhona mina, lina lingeze leza\x + 7.34.\x*?
\s Amanzi okuphila
\p
