\v 38 Okholwa kimi, njengokutsho kombhalo\x + Dute. 18.15.\x*, kuzageleza kuphuma esiswini sakhe\x + Isa. 12.3. Hez. 47.1. Zek. 14.8. Zaga 18.4.\x* imifula yamanzi aphilayo\x + 4.10.\x*.
\v 39 Lalokhu wakutsho\x + Isa. 44.3.\x* ngoMoya ababezamemukela abakholwa kuye\x + Jow. 2.28. Joha. 16.7.\x*; ngoba uMoya oNgcwele\x + Seb. 2.4,17,33,38.\x* wayengaka\add fik\add*i\x + Seb. 19.2. Joha. 1.32,33. 3.5,8,34.\x*, lokhu uJesu\x + 16.7.\x* wayengakadunyiswa\x + 12.16,23. 13.31. 17.1. 21.19.\x*.
